Nomu Cyber - Cybersecurity Bootcamp

  • Information
  • Programs (7)

What you will learn?

Learn the different network protocols and network standards

Learn the different network types and topologies

Learn Network Layer Concepts and the use of IP Addressing

Establish a strong foundation in the main pillars of Cybersecurity

Learn the potential security threats and vulnerabilities in computer systems and networks

Learn effective cybersecurity measures to protect against cyber attacks Learn to analyze and evaluate various security risks and identify appropriate solutions

Learn necessary skills in incident response in the event of a cyber attack

Be well-equipped to join top engineering teams and work with up-to-date technologies

Journey Description

The Cybersecurity Learning Journey is designed with the objective of establishing learners in the industry by providing them with a comprehensive understanding of the main pillars of Cybersecurity. 
The learning journey begins with the fundamentals of Cybersecurity and progresses toward specialized fields that are most in demand.
Throughout the program, learners will be introduced to four distinct programs: Network Fundamentals, Core Cyber Security, SOC Specialization, and Web Penetration Testing Specialization.

 

Start date: Monday 28th of August 2023

Requirements

Age: 18-35 years old

Nationality: Emiratis & Arabic-Speakers

A University degree in Engineering or Computer Science

Previous knowledge in a programming language

Good command of English

Very good problem-solving skills

Pass the selection processes
